{"word":"ἀναβιώσκομαι","slug":"ἀναβιώσκομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀναβιώσκομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>Causal of <el>ἀναβιόω.</el>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b>as <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> = <a href='S:ἀναβιόω'><el>ἀναβιόω</el></a>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>, Causal of <el>ἀναβιόω</el>, <i>to bring back to life</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>; aor1 <el>ἀνεβιωσάμην</el> <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}